<p begin="23690000t" end="38930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle0">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="40040000t" end="72690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle1">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="73740000t" end="144730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle2">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="259920000t" end="303260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle3">&#x202a;果實宣告了未知的將來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="304300000t" end="373590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle4">&#x202a;夢想蛻變成理想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="414740000t" end="496770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle5">&#x202a;任誰都渴望落幕…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="516180000t" end="531420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle6">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="532530000t" end="565180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle7">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="566230000t" end="617880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle8">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="618950000t" end="668550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle9">&#x202a;總有一天我會讓你看到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="669660000t" end="733370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle10">&#x202a;光輝閃耀的世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="811470000t" end="841730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle11">&#x202a;ICPO的各位,我是L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="842840000t" end="899500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle12">&#x202a;不管犯人是團體或是單獨一人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是日本人的可能性很高&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="900560000t" end="964840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle13">&#x202a;KIRA,我大概可以想像得到&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你為什麼要這麼做&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="965960000t" end="1000540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle14">&#x202a;但是你所做的事情是…邪惡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1001660000t" end="1032260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle15">&#x202a;這…這傢伙&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;殺了我吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1033360000t" end="1047010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle16">&#x202a;我是正義才對&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;怎麼回事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1048040000t" end="1069310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle17">&#x202a;我是拯救了弱勢族群&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1070400000t" end="1102710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle18">&#x202a;創造人人都嚮往的新世界&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;並將會成為神的男人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1107770000t" end="1117090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle19">&#x202a;L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1118110000t" end="1129030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle20">&#x202a;KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1130120000t" end="1165040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle21">&#x202a;我一定要把你找出來&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;把你解決掉&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1166160000t" end="1182770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle22">&#x202a;我是…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1189520000t" end="1198840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle23">&#x202a;正義的一方!&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1199860000t" end="1229780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle24">&#x202a;第3話 交易&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1267260000t" end="1283530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle25">&#x202a;那麼報告一般情報&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1284610000t" end="1290180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle26">&#x202a;是&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1305300000t" end="1353310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle27">&#x202a;到今天為止&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;接獲了3029件電話等一般情報&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1354350000t" end="1387340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle28">&#x202a;但大部份都是看熱鬧的民眾提供的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1388380000t" end="1434680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle29">&#x202a;有幾件指出「我知道KIRA」&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;或是「我見過KIRA」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1435760000t" end="1471370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle30">&#x202a;我們一一檢查過,並記錄下來了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1472470000t" end="1518430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle31">&#x202a;但是和報告書一樣&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;可以說沒什麼參考價值&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1519510000t" end="1568540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle32">&#x202a;另外說自己就是KIRA的有21件&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1626620000t" end="1646530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle33">&#x202a;因為不敢去除可能性&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1647640000t" end="1682560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle34">&#x202a;所以對這21人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;都作了筆錄並建檔&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1693020000t" end="1721690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle35">&#x202a;好,接著報告對被害人的調查&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1722720000t" end="1730340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle36">&#x202a;是&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1742740000t" end="1796780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle37">&#x202a;到目前為止&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這些死於心臟麻痺的被害人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1797790000t" end="1836130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle38">&#x202a;事實證明他們的身份情報&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;都能夠在日本取得&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1853510000t" end="1866130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle39">&#x202a;另外&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1867190000t" end="1909170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle40">&#x202a;L特別要求我們調查&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;推測的死亡時間&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1910240000t" end="1950510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle41">&#x202a;從日本時間週一到週五的&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;下午5點到凌晨2點&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1951610000t" end="1995300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle42">&#x202a;其中下午8點&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;到午夜0點佔了68%&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1996320000t" end="2021230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle43">&#x202a;而週六,週日和國定假日&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2022350000t" end="2055680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle44">&#x202a;則從早上11點持續到凌晨&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;時段就很分散&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2064720000t" end="2086670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle45">&#x202a;我得到相當有意思的資訊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2094420000t" end="2155400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle46">&#x202a;從死亡推定時間來看&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;犯人很有可能是學生&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2173500000t" end="2196140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle47">&#x202a;當然還有別的證據&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2197190000t" end="2257830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle48">&#x202a;從只殺犯罪者這點來看&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;犯人是基於自認的正義感而犯案&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2258920000t" end="2295890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle49">&#x202a;也許他自以為是神了吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2302960000t" end="2335610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle50">&#x202a;這是相當幼稚的心理&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2336660000t" end="2350650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle51">&#x202a;但是應該不會…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2351680000t" end="2376360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle52">&#x202a;這只是我的推測&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2377370000t" end="2430390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle53">&#x202a;但是請拋棄&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;學生一定不是犯人的既定觀念&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2431420000t" end="2455760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle54">&#x202a;不能排除所有的可能性&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2456780000t" end="2485450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle55">&#x202a;這才是逮捕「KIRA」的捷徑&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2495820000t" end="2512770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle56">&#x202a;請繼續調查報告&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2530520000t" end="2539160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle57">&#x202a;好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2548210000t" end="2566520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle58">&#x202a;還有注意到什麼問題嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2577240000t" end="2587820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle59">&#x202a;我有&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2588910000t" end="2602900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle60">&#x202a;什麼事,松田&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2621280000t" end="2668950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle61">&#x202a;我絕對沒有要肯定KIRA的意思&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2670000000t" end="2717670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle62">&#x202a;但最近世界上…特別是日本&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2718710000t" end="2749990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle63">&#x202a;強盜殺人之類的犯罪件數&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;急劇減少&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2783440000t" end="2830430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle64">&#x202a;或許該說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這也是理所當然的變化&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2836500000t" end="2846390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle65">&#x202a;還有其它的嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2883880000t" end="2915510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle66">&#x202a;今天的搜查報告就這麼多了,L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2922250000t" end="2935900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle67">&#x202a;各位辛苦了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2936930000t" end="2961840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle68">&#x202a;我覺得我更加接近犯人了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2968630000t" end="3004240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle69">&#x202a;抱歉,我還有個要求&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3005330000t" end="3044920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle70">&#x202a;特別是被害人組,新聞組,網路組&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3046040000t" end="3115100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle71">&#x202a;請你們再次調查被害人的消息&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;在日本是如何被報導的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3116110000t" end="3167080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle72">&#x202a;我想知道被害人有沒有&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;被公佈過照片或是影像&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3168160000t" end="3181130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle73">&#x202a;拜託各位了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3209530000t" end="3218170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle74">&#x202a;局長&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3232890000t" end="3253480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle75">&#x202a;您看起來很累的樣子&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3265920000t" end="3303230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle76">&#x202a;不好意思,這幾天都在熬夜&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3342330000t" end="3366670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle77">&#x202a;我剛剛說「犯罪減少了」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3367690000t" end="3402270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle78">&#x202a;其實這是大家都知道的事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3403400000t" end="3419670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle79">&#x202a;對不起&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3420750000t" end="3439060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle80">&#x202a;你在說什麼啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3440100000t" end="3469450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle81">&#x202a;不管什麼事&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;只要是事實就要說出來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3476130000t" end="3499790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle82">&#x202a;尤其是大家覺得&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;不好開口的問題&#x202c;</p>
